# DD Forge AI â€” Driver Generation Flask App

DD Forge AI is a Flask-based web application for generating, integrating, and packaging device drivers for SoCs based on user-selected interface, device, and OS type. It supports AI-assisted driver generation, Docker-based SDK building, and Redis + Celery task queue for background processing.

---

## ğŸ”§ Features

- ğŸ“„ Flask frontend to submit driver generation requests.
- ğŸ§  Remote AI-based driver generation via SSH.
- ğŸ³ Dockerfile auto-update and SDK build inside containers.
- ğŸ› ï¸ Integration with GitHub-based driver repository.
- ğŸ“¦ SDK output is compressed and made downloadable.
- ğŸª„ Celery + Redis used for background job queuing and cancellation.
- ğŸ“œ SQLAlchemy ORM with PostgreSQL for job tracking.

---

